1. *Akcija* je već započela. (The action has already started.)
2. Odlučili smo da uzmemo učešće u *akciji*. (We decided to take part in the action.)
3. Društvo je organizovalo *akciju* za pomoć siromašnima. (The society organized an action to help the poor.)
4. *Akcija* je bila uspešna. (The action was successful.)
5. Potrebna je brza *akcija*. (Quick action is needed.)
6. Pogledajte šta se dešava u *akciji*. (Look what is happening in the action.)
7. *Akcija* je bila usmerena na poboljšanje životnog standarda. (The action was directed at improving the standard of living.)